            "master": 0.8,
            "sfx": []
          }
        },
        "notes": "You arrive separately to find a country crossroads under an overcast sky with a weathered wooden signpost pointing toward a distant city\n\nThere is a long caravan of refugees with handcarts trudging west along a rutted dirt road\n\nYou see a thick column of black smoke rising far to the east over low hills; scrubby grass and shallow ditches lining the road\n\nAs you stand there watching the progression, an old woman pauses to speak with you.",
        "timeline": {
          "background": {
            "at": 800,
            "ramp": 2000
          }
        }
      },
      {
